fields.name: Akko 3098B
fields.description: The Akko 3098B is a versatile 98-key mechanical keyboard that balances functionality and compactness. It features high-quality Akko switches, RGB backlighting, and PBT keycaps for a durable and enjoyable typing experience.

fields.name: Keychron K6
fields.description: The Keychron K6 is a compact 65% mechanical keyboard that offers both wired and wireless connectivity. It features hot-swappable switches, RGB backlighting, and an ergonomic design for comfortable typing.

fields.name: Keychron K8
fields.description: The Keychron K8 is a tenkeyless (TKL) mechanical keyboard that offers both wired and wireless connectivity. It features hot-swappable switches, RGB backlighting, and a durable aluminum frame.

fields.name: CIDOO ABM098
fields.description: The CIDOO ABM098 is a full-sized mechanical keyboard with a premium build quality. It features customizable RGB backlighting, durable PBT keycaps, and a comfortable typing experience.

fields.name: Epomaker SK61
fields.description: The Epomaker SK61 is a 60% compact mechanical keyboard featuring hot-swappable switches, RGB backlighting, and durable PBT keycaps. It's designed for both portability and performance.
